    <title>桑の葉ふりかけ</title>
    <author>
      <name>山田哲也</name>
    </author>
    <content type="html">
      <![CDATA[<p class="recipe_overview">出がらしにも栄養があります。</p>
<h2 class="h2-border">材料</h2>
<ul class="ul-ingredients">
<li>
<span class="ingredients"><a href="/products/kobashitaste">桑茶<span style="font-size: small;">（ティーバッグタイプ）</span></a></span><span class="amount">1パック</span>
</li>
<li>
<span class="ingredients">白ごま</span><span class="amount">適量</span>
</li>
<li>
<span class="ingredients">塩</span><span class="amount">ひとつまみ</span>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="h2-border">作り方</h2>
