<span class="ingredients">★薄力粉</span><span class="amount">50g</span>
</li>
<li>
<span class="ingredients">★長芋</span><span class="amount">50g</span>
</li>
<li>
<span class="ingredients">★卵</span><span class="amount">1個</span>
</li>
<li>
<span class="ingredients">★和風だし（顆粒）</span><span class="amount">小さじ1/2</span>
