<span class="ingredients">ミツバ</span><br> <span class="amount">適量</span>
</li>
<li>
<a href="/products/ryokuchataste"><span class="ingredients">くつろぎタイムに緑茶風味の桑茶（ティーバッグタイプ）</span></a><br> <span class="amount">1パック</span>
